---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="Disclaimer" 
  description="Important disclaimers regarding medical, legal, and informational content on Exotic Pet Atlas."
  keywords="disclaimer, medical disclaimer, legal disclaimer, liability"
  noindex={true}
>
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-6">Disclaimer</h1>
    
    <div class="bg-red-50 border-l-4 border-red-500 p-6 rounded-lg mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">‚ö†Ô∏è IMPORTANT - PLEASE READ CAREFULLY</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700">
        The information provided on Exotic Pet Atlas is for general informational and educational purposes only. It is not intended as a substitute for professional veterinary advice, legal counsel, or expert consultation.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-8 mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">Medical/Veterinary Disclaimer</h2>
      
      <div class="bg-yellow-50 border-l-4 border-yellow-400 p-6 rounded mb-6">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">NOT VETERINARY ADVICE</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-3">
          <strong>The pet care information on this website is NOT veterinary medical advice and should NOT be used as a substitute for professional veterinary consultation, diagnosis, or treatment.</strong>
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">
          Always seek the advice of a licensed veterinarian, preferably one specializing in exotic animals, with any questions regarding your pet's health, behavior, or medical conditions.
        </p>
      </div>

      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-pastel-blue mb-3">What This Means</h3>
      <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-700">
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <span class="text-red-500 mr-2 mt-1">‚ö†</span>
          <span><strong>Emergencies:</strong> If your pet shows signs of illness or distress, contact an exotic animal veterinarian immediately. Do not rely on internet information for emergency care.</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <span class="text-red-500 mr-2 mt-1">‚ö†</span>
          <span><strong>Diagnosis:</strong> We cannot diagnose conditions based on descriptions or photos. Only a licensed veterinarian can properly diagnose your pet.</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <span class="text-red-500 mr-2 mt-1">‚ö†</span>
          <span><strong>Treatment:</strong> Never administer medications or treatments without veterinary guidance. Dosages and treatments vary by species, age, and condition.</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <span class="text-red-500 mr-2 mt-1">‚ö†</span>
          <span><strong>Individual Variation:</strong> Every animal is unique. Care requirements may differ based on genetics, health status, and environmental factors.</span>
        </li>
      </ul>

      <div class="bg-blue-50 p-6 rounded mt-6">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">Find a Qualified Veterinarian</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-3">
          Exotic animals require specialized veterinary care. Look for veterinarians with:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 text-sm space-y-1">
          <li>Board certification in exotic companion mammals, avian, or reptile/amphibian practice (ABVP)</li>
          <li>Membership in relevant organizations (ARAV, AEMV, AAV)</li>
          <li>Documented experience with your specific species</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mt-3 text-sm">
          Use our <a href="/vets/" class="text-pastel-blue hover:underline">Exotic Veterinarian Directory</a> as a starting point, but always verify credentials.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-8 mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">Legal Disclaimer</h2>
      
      <div class="bg-yellow-50 border-l-4 border-yellow-400 p-6 rounded mb-6">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">NOT LEGAL ADVICE</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-3">
          <strong>The legal information on this website is NOT legal advice and should NOT be used as a substitute for consultation with a qualified attorney or government official.</strong>
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">
          Laws governing exotic pet ownership are complex, vary by jurisdiction, and change frequently.
        </p>
      </div>

      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-pastel-blue mb-3">Important Legal Considerations</h3>
      <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-700">
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <span class="text-red-500 mr-2 mt-1">‚öñ</span>
          <span><strong>Verify Current Laws:</strong> Laws change. Always verify current regulations with your state wildlife agency, local animal control, or attorney before acquiring an exotic pet.</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <span class="text-red-500 mr-2 mt-1">‚öñ</span>
          <span><strong>Multiple Jurisdictions:</strong> State, county, city, and HOA rules may all apply. Check all relevant authorities.</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <span class="text-red-500 mr-2 mt-1">‚öñ</span>
          <span><strong>Permit Requirements:</strong> Even if an animal is legal, permits, licenses, or inspections may be required.</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <span class="text-red-500 mr-2 mt-1">‚öñ</span>
          <span><strong>Interstate Transport:</strong> Moving exotic pets across state lines may require additional permits or be prohibited entirely.</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <span class="text-red-500 mr-2 mt-1">‚öñ</span>
          <span><strong>Consequences:</strong> Illegal possession can result in fines, confiscation of animals, or criminal charges.</span>
        </li>
      </ul>

      <div class="bg-blue-50 p-6 rounded mt-6">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">Where to Verify Laws</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 text-sm space-y-1">
          <li>State Department of Fish & Wildlife / Natural Resources</li>
          <li>State Department of Agriculture</li>
          <li>County animal control offices</li>
          <li>City/municipal code enforcement</li>
          <li>Homeowners association (if applicable)</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mt-3 text-sm">
          Our <a href="/laws/" class="text-pastel-blue hover:underline">State Laws section</a> provides official source links for each state.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-8 mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">General Information Disclaimer</h2>
      
      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-pastel-blue mb-3">Accuracy and Completeness</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
        While we strive to provide accurate and up-to-date information:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-2">
        <li>Information may become outdated between updates</li>
        <li>Errors or omissions may occur despite our best efforts</li>
        <li>Content is based on available research and expert input, which evolves over time</li>
        <li>Individual circumstances may require different approaches than those described</li>
      </ul>

      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-pastel-blue mb-3 mt-6">No Guarantees</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-700">
        We make no warranties or guarantees about:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-2">
        <li>Outcomes of following our care recommendations</li>
        <li>Suitability of any particular species for your situation</li>
        <li>Quality or reliability of listed veterinarians or breeders</li>
        <li>Availability or performance of recommended products</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-8 mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">Third-Party Disclaimer</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
        Our website contains:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-2">
        <li><strong>External links:</strong> We are not responsible for content on third-party websites</li>
        <li><strong>Veterinary listings:</strong> Inclusion does not constitute endorsement of any specific practice</li>
        <li><strong>Breeder directories:</strong> Listings are informational; we do not verify breeding practices</li>
        <li><strong>Product recommendations:</strong> We are not responsible for product quality, safety, or suitability</li>
        <li><strong>Affiliate links:</strong> We may earn commissions from purchases, but this does not affect our recommendations</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-8 mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">Animal Welfare Disclaimer</h2>
      <div class="bg-green-50 p-6 rounded">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">üêæ Responsible Ownership</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-3">
          Exotic pet ownership is a serious commitment requiring:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 text-sm space-y-1">
          <li>Extensive research before acquisition</li>
          <li>Appropriate housing, diet, and veterinary care</li>
          <li>Long-term financial and time commitment</li>
          <li>Compliance with all applicable laws</li>
          <li>Contingency planning for the animal's entire lifespan</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mt-3 text-sm">
          <strong>Not all exotic animals make suitable pets.</strong> Consider rescue/adoption before purchasing, and never release exotic animals into the wild.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-8 mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">Limitation of Liability</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
        <strong>TO THE FULLEST EXTENT PERMITTED BY LAW:</strong>
      </p>
      <p class="text-gray-700">
        Exotic Pet Atlas, its owners, contributors, and affiliates are NOT LIABLE for any damages, injuries, losses, or legal consequences arising from:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 mt-3 space-y-2">
        <li>Use or reliance on information provided on this website</li>
        <li>Errors, inaccuracies, or omissions in content</li>
        <li>Animal health issues or veterinary emergencies</li>
        <li>Legal violations or consequences of exotic pet ownership</li>
        <li>Interactions with listed veterinarians, breeders, or other third parties</li>
        <li>Product purchases or equipment failures</li>
        <li>Any other matter related to the use of this website</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-8 mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">Updates and Changes</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700">
        This disclaimer may be updated periodically. Continued use of the website constitutes acceptance of the current disclaimer. Please review this page regularly.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-pastel-beige rounded-lg p-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">Questions or Concerns?</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
        If you have questions about this disclaimer or need clarification:
      </p>
      <a href="/contact/" class="inline-block bg-pastel-green text-gray-800 font-semibold px-6 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-opacity-80 transition">
        Contact Us
      </a>
    </div>

    <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-8 text-center">
      Last updated: January 18, 2026
    </p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
